title: $:/plugins/linonetwo/digital-garden/language/en-GB/

Name: Digital Garden
Readme: ! Digital Garden\n\nA 45-degree isometric city builder game.\n\nConsume rewards from the tw-gamification framework to build your knowledge city — place buildings, attract residents, bind knowledge tiddlers, and explore your city as the lord.
Description: A 45-degree isometric builder game built on the tw-gamification framework, turning real-world rewards into city-building resources.
ConfigDescription: Customize the Digital Garden plugin behavior with these settings.
Configs/Economy/Caption: Economy Settings
Configs/Economy/CopperPerSmallReward/Description: Copper coins gained per small reward
Configs/Economy/GoldPerLargeReward/Description: Gold coins gained per large reward
Configs/Economy/GoldToSilverRate/Description: Gold to silver exchange rate (1 gold = N silver)
Configs/Economy/SilverToCopperRate/Description: Silver to copper exchange rate (1 silver = N copper)
Configs/Grid/Caption: Map Settings
Configs/Grid/TileSize/Description: Tile pixel size (isometric diamond width)
Currency/Copper: Copper
Currency/Gold: Gold
Currency/Silver: Silver
Lord/Level: Lord Level
Lord/Exp: Lord EXP
World/Flat: Flat World
World/Flat/Description: A flat expanse of land, the starting point for your garden.
BuildingCategory/Learning: Learning & Reading
BuildingCategory/Rest: Rest & Recovery
BuildingCategory/Display: Display & Monument
BuildingCategory/Social: Social & Entertainment
BuildingCategory/Decoration: Decoration
BuildingCategory/Terrain: Terrain
Blueprint/Bookshelf/Caption: Bookshelf
Blueprint/Bookshelf/Description: An elegant bookshelf that can hold your knowledge tiddlers for residents to read.
Blueprint/Bench/Caption: Bench
Blueprint/Bench/Description: A bench for residents to rest and recover energy.
Blueprint/Noticeboard/Caption: Noticeboard
Blueprint/Noticeboard/Description: A noticeboard showing tiddler summaries that attracts browsing residents.
Placement/Confirm: Place
Placement/Cancel: Cancel Placement
Placement/Delete: Delete
Placement/Rotate: Rotate
Economy/Unlock/Blueprint: Unlock Blueprint
Economy/Unlock/World: Unlock World
Economy/Insufficient/Copper: Not enough copper
Economy/Insufficient/Gold: Not enough gold
Economy/Insufficient/Silver: Not enough silver
Economy/Unlock/LevelRequired: Requires Lord Level {level}
Building/Operation/Running: Running
Building/Operation/Paused: Paused
Building/Operation/Toggle: Toggle Operation
Resident/Using: Using
Content/ViewTiddler: View Tiddler
Content/Summary: Summary
Toolbar/Exit: Exit Garden
Toolbar/Move: Move
Toolbar/Place: Place
Toolbar/Select: Inspect
Toolbar/Delete: Delete
Status/MoveMode: 🚶 Move Mode
Status/PlaceMode: 🔨 Place Mode
Status/SelectMode: 🔍 Inspect Mode
Status/DeleteMode: 🗑️ Delete Mode
Status/MoveHint: Left-drag to pan · Scroll to zoom · Click tile to move lord
Status/PlaceHint: Left-click to place · Right-click/Esc to cancel · R to rotate
Status/SelectHint: Click a building to view details
Status/DeleteHint: Click a building to delete
